 />\n點知持相反立場嘅post一樣都係過千正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成鳩日發生架啦"},{"pid":"4501ebd314a80c82503e8f6a5444a423293019c8","tid":1670171,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔去加泰？<br />\n去英領！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【上議辯論造勢大會】<br />\n10月23日（三）<br />\n英國領事館門口<br />\n19：30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5iHJGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5iHJGT.jpg&h=30a60c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d70b59e7b6989a97c9fe1ce5ec6611fb9a76dc8","tid":1670171,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食住個勢 connect全世界<br />\n求搞手<br />\n求下各位推行動po</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食住個勢 connect全世界<br />\n求搞手<br />\n求下各位推行動po</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食住個勢 connect全世界<br />\n求搞手<br />\n求下各位推行動po</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"02df0602f86ebdd25c8772b87f1c50d9046cec89","tid":1670171,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7154ef9b41656133217f27924a8f4cd3fd1177","tid":1670171,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a562ffe24156b53d71b226a8ba70e06e6b049d","tid":1670171,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf4d45c879dad7e464e35b7049df0c15df49bf2","tid":1670171,"uid":48631,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"我自己就唔會去加泰集會嘅，但唔明做乜有班友喺度攻擊搞手又叫佢要取消集會<br />\n唔鍾意去就咪去囉，點解要叫人取消<br />\n當正自己大台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割 但搞集會就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"唔啱佢地心水就係鬼黎架啦，成班單細胞生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa437d16c1ba58bb77f5ee36e4fe4e6352cf40","tid":1670171,"uid":237342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"唔洗理 由佢地慢慢屌<br />\n唔會去 但係睇唔撚慣一邊屌lbj一邊自己做一樣既野<br />\n為左人權法就將反警暴集會強行link落撐獨立<br />\n黑警反對遊行就屌人因為主題係解散警隊為自己利益反對<br />\n宜家屌人去集會我真係唔知到底乜野標準<br />\n<br />\n美國過撚左人權法個運動都唔會贏<br />\n最多都係多樣武器（睇區選未有DQ就知）<br />\n對家已經有對策黎種票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登就成班係到搞分化<br />\n<br />\n成件事好簡單 未集會前去twitter做文宣（做緊）<br />\n集會召集人讓一步撐全球反警暴<br />\n屌人叫人唔好去一d都唔實際<br />\n不斷開po屌人不如做下實事好過<br />\n唔期待會感化到班傻鳩<br />\n我真係寧願佢地去查案<br />\n起碼叫做有d貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f675f38d5a922c7854b884dfc030878aaaf198a4","tid":1670171,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"睇埋支那01報導 就知今日中共用左幾多人力黎係加泰呢件事上面做手腳<br />\n<br />\n一早講 兄弟龜山 各有各做<br />\n<br />\n依家班蠢人就俾五毛又帶風向去屌撐加泰既手足<br />\n<br />\n唉 香港輸在蠢人太多"},{"pid":"08f45680e4b0b1593cdcfaba76cf2b17b37cc737","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cd261133ae2f20d034c953e22350e33208cdfbf","tid":1670171,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9864ca32652429fa73fd712b4ed302a0d46aaf1d","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c006b75126bcc3dccaa60ea459079cab72677255","tid":1670171,"uid":11254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"班傻西日日講咩共識<br />\n共你老母咩<br />\n連登都係得幾萬USER<br />\n都唔撚知佢地共識點樣黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:12:31.000Z","msg":"係連登提出「前線共識」係最on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地知共識伏伏地，依家用「軍規」，不過都冇人理"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"所以而加前線都唔會用連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCC台開個POST就當做左野架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"前線睇連登會人格分裂，思覺失調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fffb6e3bd63160686215592b24acfbf168b8d7","tid":1670171,"uid":272096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"［加泰集會］駁到我先講唔好去集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670203</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"704c7a7c91ccd99f058019a80ef48013eb3ed76a","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e41ffdf430b37f2a9a1836f282491bd702769ed3","tid":1670171,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"HK01風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"好似真係得支共01講加泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac818ba98481ff6528cc0914ae85868b4958e75","tid":1670171,"uid":25968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"d5aef751d7bb66a3f829689d03947bbabc9e4ad4","tid":1670171,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4af414a7c5a6ac923ee72766d984a87ce70878","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"連人鏈都冇人既時候<br />\n首先加泰個集會就肯定冇咩人去<br />\n第二就係外國邊個得閒理鳩你去唔去<br />\n所以係搵黎拗<br />\n有咩人會搵野黎拗？自己諗<br />\n<br />\n0.3一路想做既野<br />\n就係搵一d大家「共識」唔會做既野<br />\n然後就瘋狂攻擊做既人，指責，分化割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如「共識」唔拆鐵，你睇依家大家幾開心<br />\n「共識」唔塞鐵，你夠膽依家問多次<br />\n「共識」唔玩火，「共識」唔陣地，「共識」唔魔化</span><br />\n<br />\n分化一班人好簡單<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就係首先製造「共識」</span><br />\n然後就指責違反既人破壞運動<br />\n可以嘈足三日三夜<br />\n<br />\n一路以黎運動維持至今<br />\n都係因為我地冇理呢d共識（核彈都唔割）<br />\n0.3又重施故技，主題「唔好得罪國際」<br />\n本質玩法同2014「唔好得罪共產黨」一樣<br />\n都係話咩要對家做野，就唔好得罪佢<br />\n而「得罪條件」係層出不窮<br />\n包括<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好舉美國旗」「唔好勇武，要休息」「唔好叫Trump」</span><br />\n最後證明全部係廢話<br />\n事實係對家做野只在乎利益<br />\n根本唔care咩加泰集會<br />\n製造咁多「唔好」目的都係想分化一部分人<br />\n<br />\n去就去，唔去就唔去<br />\n各有各做<br />\n外國好多野做，唔得閒理你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"文章值得一學<br />\n學完就可以分化對面了"},{"pid":"133421dde896aea041c6e2da9acfe24245657206","tid":1670171,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"口交部:請歐美聽香港人民意，回應加泰人民訴求，勿搞雙標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"653694b974cd08e8b772b9c14fba8a4f14145fde","tid":1670171,"uid":81531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:29:16.000Z","msg":"屌你 開頭唔撚搞咁多野咪算囉"},{"pid":"e90d73ea81de32cbd7b0bf35dafe305304573d52","tid":1670171,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"Solomon 唔係都叫我地唔好搞加泰咩"},{"pid":"661ac8716b0a7f5bc6d1d60a6326f848cea0fabc","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a562ffe24156b53d71b226a8ba70e06e6b049d","tid":1670171,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf4d45c879dad7e464e35b7049df0c15df49bf2","tid":1670171,"uid":48631,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"我自己就唔會去加泰集會嘅，但唔明做乜有班友喺度攻擊搞手又叫佢要取消集會<br />\n唔鍾意去就咪去囉，點解要叫人取消<br />\n當正自己大台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割 但搞集會就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割，但係唔啱心水就割"},{"pid":"85f6b4bdc7c2b21f7e1a9637feea59e5d2f28b38","tid":1670171,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90d73ea81de32cbd7b0bf35dafe305304573d52","tid":1670171,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"Solomon 唔係都叫我地唔好搞加泰咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"Solomon 都叫唔好裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd6a4c75b5e7c371e8b8086868dfab951ceef4c","tid":1670171,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4af414a7c5a6ac923ee72766d984a87ce70878","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"連人鏈都冇人既時候<br />\n首先加泰個集會就肯定冇咩人去<br />\n第二就係外國邊個得閒理鳩你去唔去<br />\n所以係搵黎拗<br />\n有咩人會搵野黎拗？自己諗<br />\n<br />\n0.3一路想做既野<br />\n就係搵一d大家「共識」唔會做既野<br />\n然後就瘋狂攻擊做既人，指責，分化割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如「共識」唔拆鐵，你睇依家大家幾開心<br />\n「共識」唔塞鐵，你夠膽依家問多次<br />\n「共識」唔玩火，「共識」唔陣地，「共識」唔魔化</span><br />\n<br />\n分化一班人好簡單<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就係首先製造「共識」</span><br />\n然後就指責違反既人破壞運動<br />\n可以嘈足三日三夜<br />\n<br />\n一路以黎運動維持至今<br />\n都係因為我地冇理呢d共識（核彈都唔割）<br />\n0.3又重施故技，主題「唔好得罪國際」<br />\n本質玩法同2014「唔好得罪共產黨」一樣<br />\n都係話咩要對家做野，就唔好得罪佢<br />\n而「得罪條件」係層出不窮<br />\n包括<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好舉美國旗」「唔好勇武，要休息」「唔好叫Trump」</span><br />\n最後證明全部係廢話<br />\n事實係對家做野只在乎利益<br />\n根本唔care咩加泰集會<br />\n製造咁多「唔好」目的都係想分化一部分人<br />\n<br />\n去就去，唔去就唔去<br />\n各有各做<br />\n外國好多野做，唔得閒理你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6ac5a206d8113521ce16bec4ab7fdb436e48d6f7","tid":1670171,"uid":265534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b92b9c6d1ac713e2e6468ea03dd3fa833dbbb8","tid":1670171,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"認同樓主<br />\n<br />\n唔好既post全部唔洗睇"},{"pid":"e452d4f1238408372fb8b32760e67e764b188c5a","tid":1670171,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"519cfba983740790439855fd34152e2bb4fda775","tid":1670171,"uid":180317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"去就去<br />\n唔去就唔去<br />\n利申：我支持加泰獨立但係唔會去集會，屌你我哋自己都未搞掂"},{"pid":"9677e43d9afb4ddc589c6d4c82aed7baab5c08e7","tid":1670171,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"咁家下即係點?<br />\n啲風向吹到好煩<br />\n真心唔想搞到條法案過唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條法案家下搞到變左我地春袋"},{"pid":"c4e3b9a01d18ccdaac552d448f1aa14bd59cdf9c","tid":1670171,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"以後叫人唔好X，唔好Y，唔好Z，一律當係hk01分化post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669478</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1587eeedd4a3a0574fa406000f07fa622536df0","tid":1670171,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"自己唔去，唔好阻人去"},{"pid":"89caf504bb94169d1512e3f252ec1bf425962cbc","tid":1670171,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"外面反加泰集會反得有點誇張<br />\n但樓主你講野邏輯都有問題<br />\n<blockquote>都係因為我地冇理呢d共識</blockquote><br />\n以偏概全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無視部份共識就係無視全部？<br />\n不偷不搶唔係遵守緊既共識？<br />\n暫時唔提港獨唔係又係目前共識？<br />\n不割不分不篤灰咪一樣係一種共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而「得罪條件」係層出不窮<br />\n包括「唔好舉美國旗」「唔好勇武，要休息」「唔好叫Trump」<br />\n最後證明全部係廢話</blockquote><br />\n叫人揮美國旗同向Trump求援既陳雲，都話要叫停加泰集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得唔洗停集會，但要叫出席者唔好揮加泰獨立旗，改揮加泰地區旗<br />\n<br />\n點解係都要將違反自己見解既說法叫成「帶風向」？<br />\n我覺得呢種諗法比「帶風向」本身更具破壞力<br />\n點解唔坦然接受真係有好多人同自己意見唔同？<br />\n<br />\n九月頭時我話應該要搞和理非大遊行，成班衝出黎鬧我係鬼係五毛係mon post狗<br />\n結果一個二個最後咪又係要求民陣搞大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我都從來唔會話有人帶風向反鳩我，因為事實係大家當時同我意見唔同，咁我當時都坦然接受唔再堅持落去"},{"pid":"02fb1649963bda0265369a65efa334362bc37102","tid":1670171,"uid":73026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:39:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"196657e606ed2bf375d3a390422829c031f690ce","tid":1670171,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/72768335_2473808126038251_6978876850143494144_n_ZiI2v_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F72768335_2473808126038251_6978876850143494144_n_ZiI2v_1200x0.jpg&h=63253f5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b584ac3d1c52c3cdfedf02658bcb8f4a975e6f","tid":1670171,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解睇得美國同歐盟既 LIP SERVICES 咁緊要<br />\n<br />\n到目前為止, 都只係 LIP SERVICES<br />\n<br />\n香港係支美貿易戰其中一粒棋<br />\n隨時也有可能被美帝放棄同支共換利益<br />\n正如1982年英國做法一樣<br />\n<br />\n你睇下庫爾德就知, 美帝都唔可以100%盲信"},{"pid":"4880dac816d45c508c791e927ba2c73169cb0761","tid":1670171,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"小心呀一陣又有人衝入嚟話你帶風向㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5519b463ebb532eae115f13f177e56decd5f36","tid":1670171,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"唔講贊唔贊成<br />\n攻擊搞手攻到體無完膚<br />\n咩三毛 01 共諜內鬼臥底<br />\n如果我係搞手一定心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n二來香港人天真夠未<br />\n死咗咁多手足<br />\n幾時先可以將獨立放上枱面講？<br />\n根本香港就有法理獨立<br />\n大把前英殖民地獨立咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老實實無論你五大訴求定雙普選<br />\n老共一早都標籤咗成場運動係港獨㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係以為唔講出口會打得輕手啲下話<br />\n<br />\n不過好明顯有班人係故意分化<br />\n乘住我地有少少分歧就煲大佢<br />\n用字有咁難聽得咁難聽<br />\n扮晒兩邊咁開火<br />\n點鬧都好<br />\n都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬧到過晒火嗰啲就要 block 了"},{"pid":"e0cf67db8393bce3176f172b9a771b4ae29d42b2","tid":1670171,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90d73ea81de32cbd7b0bf35dafe305304573d52","tid":1670171,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"Solomon 唔係都叫我地唔好搞加泰咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"Gphone話搞得"},{"pid":"3107804348c0003cd7aa64fc4eb74caecedd2a8a","tid":1670171,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a334f171ab9656716810d397afca0a0dd4366d7","tid":1670171,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n明明核彈都唔割<br />\n而家加獨就即割on99"},{"pid":"42184a08201dfaee7ea90fdcdf5dd8466d3b5a1e","tid":1670171,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fx2BoL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffx2BoL8.jpg&h=f902303d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6875283341c23f111130fb4225be83d8b4e43a16","tid":1670171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16a946991c9e38979d1293508b4ddd398eb9f0a","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"連仔應該公開放負放正名單啦<br />\n呢個po放負果30個好大機會係5毛"},{"pid":"f515ed02857beb236217c2ee688fc8a28a5bff46","tid":1670171,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42184a08201dfaee7ea90fdcdf5dd8466d3b5a1e","tid":1670171,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fx2BoL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffx2BoL8.jpg&h=f902303d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos